gov.nih.nlm.nls.lvg.Trie

Class RTrieTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nih.nlm.nls.lvg.Trie.RTrieTree

  • public class RTrieTree
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates an object of a reverse trie tree. A reverse trie trie includes a tree structure consists of trie nodes.
